Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Libyans challenge US aircraft
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043whtz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Aug 1981
President Reagan flexes his international muscles over US-Libyan air intercepts. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.